<template lang="pug">
main
  div.wrapper
   div.block(v-for='photo in photos')
      div.art
         div.ava
         a {{photo.artist}}
      div.pic {{photo.picture}}
      div.counter 51 200
       include ../assets/Eye.svg

</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: 'Work',
  data () {
    return {
      photos: [
        {
          artist: 'jason mawry  @jason_mawry_photo',
          picture: '23232'
        },
        {
          artist: 'jason mawry  @jason_mawry_photo',
          picture: '23232'
        }
        /*  {
          artist: 'jason mawry  @jason_mawry_photo',
          picture: '23232'
        } */
        /*    {
          artist: 'jason mawry  @jason_mawry_photo',
          picture: '23232'
        },
        {
          artist: 'jason mawry  @jason_mawry_photo',
          picture: '23232'
        },
        {
          artist: 'jason mawry  @jason_mawry_photo',
          picture: '23232'
        } */
      ]
    }
  },
  methods: {
  },
  computed: {
  },
  components: {
  }
}
</script>

<style lang="scss" scoped>
 main {
       width: 1000px;
       height: max-content;
       background-color: aqua;
       margin: auto;
  }
  .wrapper {
     width: 660px;
     height: 312px;
     margin: auto;
     display: flex;
  }
  .block {
     width: 320px;
     height: 312px;
     margin: auto;
  }
  .art {
    display: flex;
    width: 225px;
    height: 50px;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-around;
  }
.ava{
   width: 30px;
   height: 30px;
   border-radius: 50%;
   background-color: black;
}
.pic{
   width: 320px;
   height: 230px;
   background-color: brown;
}
.counter{
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding: 10px 10px;
    align-items: center;
}
@media (max-width: 320px){
    main {
       width: 320px;
       height: 720px;
       background-color: aqua;
       margin: auto;
  }
  .wrapper {
     width: 320px;
     height: 312px;
     margin: auto;
     display: block;
  }
  .block {
     width: 320px;
     height: 312px;
     margin: auto;
  }
  .art {
    display: flex;
    width: 225px;
    height: 50px;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-around;
  }
.ava{
   width: 30px;
   height: 30px;
   border-radius: 50%;
   background-color: black;
}
.pic{
   width: 320px;
   height: 230px;
   background-color: brown;
}
.counter{
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding: 10px 10px;
}

}
</style>
